2 HOUSE BILL 1155
1 (1) IMPROVEMENTS TO PHYSICAL, CHEMICAL, OR BIOLOGICAL
2 CHARACTERISTICS OR PROCESSES;
3 (2) RETURNING NATURAL OR HISTORICAL FUNCTIONS OR SERVICES;
4 OR
5 (3) PROTECTING OR IMPROVING RESILIENCY.
6 1–1002.
7 THE DEPARTMENT SHALL UPDATE ANY RELEVANT REGULATION ADOPTED
8 UNDER THIS ARTICLE TO, AS APPROPRIATE:
9 (1) INCORPORATE THE DEFINITION OF ECOLOGICAL RESTORATION;
10 OR
11 (2) BE CONSISTENT WITH THE DEFINITION OF ECOLOGICAL
12 RESTORATION.
13 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
14 October 1, 2025.

